    {
      "id": "1773096357638-r0tvqwm2i",
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Done! Now whenever your character dies, a forced ad will show up right before the game over screen appears. This works for both regular gameplay and auto-play mode. \n\nA couple of notes about how this works:\n- **Subscribers won't see the ad** — the platform automatically hides it for them, so no extra handling is needed.\n- **If the ad fails or isn't available**, the game over screen will still appear normally — nothing will break.\n- The ad shows up during the natural pause after death (the 800ms delay), so it feels like a natural break point rather than an interruption mid-gameplay.",
      "isShownToUser": true,
      "timestamp": 1773096364048,
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {}
